* Displays runner info for the announcer at the finish line

* Purpose:          Provides a high-contrast, color-coded screen for calling out runners.

* Where to run:     Usually run on a separate RSClient machine at the announcer station.

* When to use:      During the race, typically triggered 10-15m before the finish line.

* How it works:     Listens for the "Announcer" event and displays incoming runner details.

